ance the company’s brand image and reputation in the us and abroad through integrated media communications and marketing efforts in addition she served as a senior communications advisor to top management on business strategy acquisitions product introductions customer issues litigation and government relations from 99 to  ms trower was a managing director at jpmorgan chase where she was responsible for corporate communications at jpmorgan fleming asset management prior to that she spent  years at chancellor lgt asset management now part of invesco where she was vice president of corporate communications ms trower graduated from hollins university in roanoke va she is a member of its alumnae board of directors ms trower lives in new york city with her husband and daughter jobs updatecurrentexecutive vice president global communicationsestee lauder companiesadd board  advisor rolesadd educationadd newsadd membershipsadd imagesadd videosbcdalrjykyas5vwnu alexandra trower  international womens media foundation iwmf search navbar about us mission vision  financials press room board of directors iwmf alumni staff donors contact us privacy policy programs  opportunities iwmf emergency fund adelante english adelante español african great lakes reporting initiative participate in the initiative african great lakes reporting fellows incountry training reshaping the narrative elizabeth neuffer fellowship apply for the neuffer fellowship fund for women journalists hefat training reporting grants for women’s stories awards anja niedringhaus award  anja niedringhaus award past award winners about anja niedringhaus courage in journalism award  courage in journalism award nominate a journalist awardees 996 awardee updates issueswhat we stand for journalist safety media entrepreneurship press freedom women’s leadership research status of women in news media violence and harassment against women journalists get involved subscribe volunteer advocacy events event photos live stream so